      "text": "Ana Maria. I summoned you here to discuss long-term strategy, but we have a crisis to address. You've seen my uncle's broadcast—what Ostergaard did to Lord Karosas. What his soldiers are <i>still</i> doing to the people of Smithon below us.\n\nI am honor bound to ride to their defense.",
