      "index": 1,
      "text": "Kamea… you've got much bigger things to worry about than Smithon. I won't mince words: your cause is very nearly lost.\n\nWith only a small fraction of their fleet, the [[DM.Factions[faction_TaurianConcordat],Taurians]] have you dramatically outgunned. Given the chance, the <i>Iberia</i> alone could break your army in two.",
