      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ca7215ce964c57d5f365a71"
      },
      "index": 3,
      "text": "If you're looking for proof, I can't help you. But I can tell you what I think is behind all of this: the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LorePerditionMassacre],Perdition Massacre]].\n\nI believe that [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreHouseDavion],House Davion]]'s attack on the Concordat created an opportunity for Espinosa. And unfortunately for us, I believe that he has taken it.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "What opportunity? Spell it out for me.",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 4,
          "hideIfUnavailable": false,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c9f3a172e24f28eaaebca9a"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        },
        {
          "responseText": "You think that Espinosa offered them his support against the Federated Suns.",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 7,
          "hideIfUnavailable": false,
          "onlyOnce": false,
