    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c2ba24eb4de97c0cd66fb93"
      },
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Protector Calderon believes that a Davion invasion of the Taurian Concordat is imminent. In the Directorate, he sees a convenient pawn, and a buffer to protect a poorly-defended stretch of the Concordat's border.\n\nIf the Directorate's weapons have been coming from the Taurians, I imagine they've had an agreement in place for some time.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 5,
