      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cd287428725fb9225c47145"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Yeah… that timing makes sense. By arming the Directorate, Calderon would be fortifying his own border against invasion.\n\nWhen Espinosa learned about Castle Nautilus, he must've used it as a bargaining chip to get the Taurians into the war on his side.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 6,
