    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c541782c2c61296c6501ecf"
      },
      "index": 6,
      "text": "In a limited intervention, but yes. Calderon would've leaped at the chance to claim an [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreSLDF],SLDF]] armory… with a major war imminent, the capture of a fully-stocked [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreOutpostCastle],Outpost Castle]] could've provided the Taurians with a tremendous advantage.\n\nBut you destroyed the armory, and killed their soldiers… and, apparently, destroyed one of their DropShips on Anvelt. I suspect that your problems with the Taurian Concordat have only just begun.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 2,
