      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cb92aca7b8eba5e0b78e4d3"
      },
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Of course it is. That's why Taurian BattleMechs are sacking Smithon, even as we speak. He's trying to lure Lady Arano <i>to</i> him.\n\nIt's a deliberate provocation, Kamea. You must realize that.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 2,
          "hideIfUnavailable": false,
          "onlyOnce": false,
