    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cbab51e051d304f456b1c77"
      },
      "index": 11,
      "text": "I would advise you to lead your army wisely, and to stay out of battles you cannot win.\n\nKamea, listen to me. There is <i>still hope</i>. But you won't find it on the battlefield.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
