      "index": 12,
      "text": "The alliance between the Taurians and the Directorate is tenuous—far more so than they would have you believe.\n\n[[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreThomasCalderon],Protector Calderon]] knows what kind of man your uncle is. We could turn allies into enemies if we play our cards right.",
