      "text": "Your mercenaries have been one of your key advantages in this war, Kamea. By doing this, you're putting them at grave risk… but if your heart is set on returning to Smithon, I am powerless to stop you.\n\nInstead, I'll wish you good luck and take my leave—I'll be in touch when my agents know more. But please, Kamea… <i>stay safe</i>. I don't know if I can stabilize the Reach without you.",
